574
00:34:07,830 --> 00:34:09,930
Well, I was just stepping
into the shower,

575
00:34:09,965 --> 00:34:11,265
but how can I help you?

576
00:34:11,299 --> 00:34:14,301
I wanted to tell you
it's not worth it.

577
00:34:14,336 --> 00:34:17,338
And if we don't get
Jaguar, so what?

578
00:34:17,373 --> 00:34:20,174
Who wants to be in business
with people like that?

579
00:34:27,749 --> 00:34:28,948
How'd it go?

580
00:34:28,983 --> 00:34:31,518
We'll see.

581
00:34:31,552 --> 00:34:33,487
It was one of his good ones.

582
00:34:34,922 --> 00:34:38,323
- Come have a drink?
- Maybe later.

583
00:34:54,204 --> 00:34:57,106
- Where are you from?
- New York.

584
00:35:00,076 --> 00:35:02,911
<i>Turn around, please.</i>

585
00:35:02,946 --> 00:35:06,149
Could you step forward, sweetheart,
and turn around, please?

586
