The food's too bad.

588
00:35:24,901 --> 00:35:27,301
We're not actually gonna
eat here, are we?

589
00:35:27,335 --> 00:35:28,803
I'm not hungry.

590
00:35:28,837 --> 00:35:30,905
Freddy Rums says you are.

591
00:35:30,939 --> 00:35:32,774
And so does Tom Vogel.

592
00:35:32,808 --> 00:35:34,408
You know we have Clearasil.

593
00:35:34,442 --> 00:35:37,078
In fact, he sung your praises

594
