and I saw somebody

615
00:36:31,597 --> 00:36:34,732
who was writing like
every product was for them.

616
00:36:34,766 --> 00:36:37,635
No cliches, no homilies,

617
00:36:37,669 --> 00:36:39,837
no formula.

618
00:36:39,871 --> 00:36:42,973
Well, I had a lot of help.

619
