the same favor.

627
00:37:32,854 --> 00:37:36,690
- Oh.
- If this is your last meeting.

628
00:37:39,527 --> 00:37:42,362
I think I
need a chocolate shake.

629
00:37:44,832 --> 00:37:48,368
First day of work ends with
you and me at La Caravelle.

630
00:37:53,072 --> 00:37:56,074
- You're here.
- I'm here.

631
00:37:59,212 --> 00:38:00,546
How'd it go?

632
00:38:10,523 --> 00:38:12,524
How did yours go?

633
00:38:12,558 --> 00:38:14,693
We're waiting to hear.

634
00:38:14,727 --> 00:38:17,094
I bet you were great.

635
00:38:17,129 --> 00:38:19,897
I bet you were, too.

636
00:38:19,932 --> 00:38:23,467
The difference is
I want you to get it.

637
00:38:23,501 --> 00:38:24,702
Stop it.

638
00:38:24,736 --> 00:38:27,003
Well, you get to disappear
for work whenever you want.

639
00:38:27,038 --> 00:38:30,907
And if I have to choose
between you and that,

640
00:38:30,942 --> 00:38:34,277
I'll choose you.

641
